*Ideja* da se odemo na more je bila odlična (The idea of going to the sea was great).

*Ideju* da putujemo za Srbiju smo dobili preko prijatelja (We got the idea to travel to Serbia from a friend).

*Idejom* da se zaposlim, sam se zainteresovala (I was interested in the idea of getting a job).

*Idejama* o modernizaciji, mi se nismo slagali (We did not agree on the ideas of modernization).

*Ideje* da se napravi novi projekat, smo dobili od našeg mentora (We got the ideas to make a new project from our mentor).